### User / Order CRUD 테스트
### 1. USER 생성 (기본 데이터)

POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Smith",
  "age": 28
}

###
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Emily Johnson",
  "age": 24
}

###
### 2. USER 전체 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/users

###
### 3. ORDER 생성 (userId 필요)
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item": "MacBook Pro",
  "userId": 1
}

###
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item": "iPhone 15",
  "userId": 2
}

###
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item": "AirPods Pro",
  "userId": 1
}

###
### 4. ORDER 전체 조회 (N+1 체크 대상)
GET http://localhost:8080/orders

###
### 5. ORDER 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/1

###
### 6. ORDER 수정 (item만 변경)
PUT http://localhost:8080/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item": "MacBook Air",
  "userId": 1
}

###
### 7. ORDER 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/orders/2

###
### 8. ORDER 삭제 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/orders

###
### 9. ORDER 예외 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/999

###
### 10. USER Validation 확인
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "age": null
}

###
### 11. ORDER Validation 확인
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item": "",
  "userId": null
}